<div id="pf8db" class="pf w2 h124" data-page-no="8db"><div class="pc pc8db w2 h124"><div class="t m97c xb9 h4 y2088 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">16 </div><div class="t m5 x27 h4 y2088 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t mb26 x53 h4 y18d7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THESSALONIANS AND EPHESIANS. </div><div class="t m1fb6 xb9 h4 y1a80 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to flight. Yet Paul was willing to labor alone in the great, </div><div class="t m126 xb9 h4 y1bc4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">strange city for awhile, so that the new converts might not be </div><div class="t m12b6 x3 h4 y1baa ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">left too long. When he had left them, he was forced to flee </div><div class="t m531 x3 h4 y1a43 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">from them. Now he did not wish them to become discouraged </div><div class="t m980 xb9 h4 y1ef0 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by his afflictions or their own. </div><div class="t m2b6 x15 h4 y14c2 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m728 x18 h4 y18b2 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">David said in the Spirit, &quot;What shall I render unto the Lord </div><div class="t m1652 xb9 h4 y1d11 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for all His benefits to me?&quot; Paul counted the conversion of </div><div class="t mb73 xb9 h4 y1949 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">these souls and their steadfastness in God as benefits which God </div><div class="t m98b xb9 h4 y1c78 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">had granted him. </div><div class="t ma2 x15 h4 y1d4a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m187 x26 h4 y1994 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Abound in love one toward another.&quot; Oh. how much need </div><div class="t m83 xb9 h4 y1d4b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">there is of it! We can not abound toward others if not our </div><div class="t m72e xb9 h4 y202e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">brethren. Love grows by cultivation, by doing, by giving. He </div><div class="t m174a xb9 h4 y1e79 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">who shuts himself from ministry to his brethren can not love </div><div class="t m715 xb9 h4 y1ed9 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them. </div><div class="t m1cd x27 h4 y1e2d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m12aa x26 h4 y1af8 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;At the coming of our Lord Jesus.&quot; Literally at His </div><div class="t mc43 xb9 h4 y218b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">personal presence, for so the word means. See 2 Cor. 7:6, 7; </div><div class="t m103c x3 h4 y1f95 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to:ro. He is here now by His ambassadors, and by His Spirit; </div><div class="t me86 xb9 h4 y2147 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">but not in the sense of His promise. John 14:1-3; Acts 1:9-if. </div><div class="t m6ce xb9 h4 y2213 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">That promise will not be fulfilled until He comes in His own </div><div class="t mdad xb9 h4 y1142 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">personal presence. Then we shall see Him as He is, this &quot;same </div><div class="t m17ca xb9 h4 y16d2 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jesus.&apos; That is the hope of the church. </div><div class="t m4aa x63 h16 y1bff ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON VI.—Walking with God. </div><div class="t m77d x31 h4 y1b24 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MAY 9. </div><div class="t m11e3 x40 h4 y1a51 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I TRESS. 4:I-I2. </div><div class="t me21 x27 h4 y12ac ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(I) Finally then, brethren, we beseech and exhort you in the </div><div class="t m70f xb9 h4 y1d24 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lord Jesus, that, as ye received of us how ye ought to walk </div><div class="t m8c3 xb9 h4 y1f0a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and to please God, even as ye do walk,—that ye abound more </div><div class="t m987 xb9 h4 y1664 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and more. (2) For ye know what charge we gave you through </div><div class="t mb20 xb9 h4 y1d67 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Lord Jesus. (3) For this is the will of God, even your </div><div class="t m1fd0 xb9 h4 y1c98 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sanctification, that ye abstain from fornication; (4) that each </div><div class="t me9d xb9 h4 y1b01 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">one of you know how to possess himself of his own vessel in </div><div class="t m1588 xb9 h30 y124d ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We expend sixty per cent of our efforts upon four per cent of </div><div class="t m1480 x82 h30 y1beb ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our field. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
